txt.en: Barliman Butterbur had a letter to send you, but he misplaced it. One thing drives out another, after all! Now that he has remembered, he hopes his oversight will not cause trouble.
Barliman Butterbur hopes his oversight will not cause trouble.
Barliman Butterbur has a habit of misplacing important messages, and only recently remembered he had one such message for you.
